Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper is about automatic speech recognition (ASR) and natural language processing (NLP) using an end-to-end attention-based encoder-decoder model. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also likely as the paper deals with processing raw speech waveform. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses deep learning techniques such as feature transfer learning and attention-based models. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible as the paper deals with developing an AI system for speech recognition.
